text: Prince Kosi Samuzu (born 6 March 1993)Judo - Prince Kosi Samuzu. Les-sports is a Democratic Republic of the Congo judoka. He competed at the 2019 African Games, winning a bronze medal in the men's –100 kg category. He also competed in the 2015 African Games but did not win a medal.KOSI SAMUZU PRINCE.
